				<div class="comment-body"><p>Hello,</p>
<p>I&#8217;m just curious whether the Hugo Award ceremony was going to be streamed on the Internet this year. I&#8217;ve tried looking for info, but haven&#8217;t found any, so I&#8217;m assuming not, but it would be cool to be able to see it live. This might not be the proper place to ask, but I figured you guys might know, haha. Anyway, thanks a bunch. I&#8217;m looking forward to learning the results. </p>
<p>Cheers,<br />
Christopher Nickolas Carlson</p>
