		<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-24427">
		<div id="comment-24427">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/9b8152488ad03082b2183a772f9489a4?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/9b8152488ad03082b2183a772f9489a4?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn"><a href='http://thegrinder.diabolicalplots.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>David Steffen</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
