				<div class="comment-body"><p>Thomas:</p>
<p>While there have been <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Hugo_Award_anthologies" title="Wikipedia Entry on 'The Hugo Winners' Collections" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">compilations of Hugo Award-winning fiction</a> in the past, there have not been recent collections except for <em><a href="../../2009/11/introducing-the-hugo-award-showcase/index.html" title="Announcement of 2010 Hugo Award Showcase" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">The Hugo Award Showcase</a></em>, the first (and ultimately only) in a projected series of collections of Hugo Award-nominated-and-winning works. Should a publisher once again undertake publishing such compilations, we will announce it on this site.</p>
