		<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-81000">
		<div id="comment-81000">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6091fb17f3d194d0504fbfe17375a787?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6091fb17f3d194d0504fbfe17375a787?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn">Kathleen Hopper</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
