				<div class="comment-body"><p>The materials in the packet are standard e-reader and PDF documents, they will not erase themselves.  Items in the packet are only available to voters to download and only while the voting period is open.  Once the voting period closes, the download functions will be disabled.</p>
<p>It is possible this technology could change in future years, this is how it is done now.</p>
</div>

