				<div class="comment-body"><p>Sam: Yes, self-published works are eligible for the Hugo Award. The <a href="http://www.wsfs.org/bm/rules.html" title="WSFS Rules" rel="nofollow">WSFS rules</a> do not specify how a work is published, only that it is published.</p>
</div>

