				<div class="comment-body"><p>Nana: Our reply to your other question about &#8220;Jodorowsky’s Dune&#8221; applies here as well: the first US publication of the work in 2014 gives the work an additional year of eligibility in 2015 due to the newly-adopted rule regarding publication outside of the US.</p>
</div>

