			<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="index.html#comment-321425">
				January 29, 2015 at 14:57					</a>
									</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->

				<div class="comment-body"><p>In general, fiction anthologies are not eligible for any category. The individual works published in the anthology may be eligible in the appropriate &#8220;story&#8221; category if they first appeared in the eligibility year. If they are reprints of older stories, they are not eligible unless they have been substantially revised.</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=321425#respond' data-commentid="321425" data-postid="11" data-belowelement="comment-321425" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Kevin'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
