				<div class="comment-body"><p>We are not actively chasing down older information, but when it becomes available, we post it to the site. WSFS rules have not always required the disclosure of the &#8220;They Also Ran&#8221; information, and in many years there was nothing more than the list of finalists and the final ballot counts.</p>
<p>If anyone has the information for prior years and could share it with us, we&#8217;d be happy to add it to the historical data.</p>
