				<div class="comment-body"><p>Has a separate award for non-English works been considered? I think (as I shortly argue in the link) that they&#8217;ve been rather drastically overlooked in the past (it&#8217;s a good sign that &#8220;Three-Body Problem&#8221; got a nom this year). It wouldn&#8217;t preclude them from the existing categories, but be an addition (just as a movie can, theoretically, win &#8220;Best Picture&#8221; and &#8220;Best Foreign Film&#8221; at the Oscars).</p>
<p>Selfishly, this would hopefully allow me to discover new works I wouldn&#8217;t normally hear about!</p>
<p>Thanks!</p>
</div>

