				<div class="comment-body"><p>First public showing of a movie would include film festivals. In the case you cite, the movie would appear to have been eligible for the 2015 Hugo Awards. The 2015 WSFS Business Meeting would have needed to pass a resolution extending its eligibility (they did so for &#8220;Predestination&#8221;). However, it&#8217;s now too late for that. I think the work has exhausted its eligibility.</p>
</div>

