<p> Worldcons don&#8217;t publish copies of the nominated works. If someone wants to issue a translation of the work, that&#8217;s up to them and whoever owns the rights, if it&#8217;s still in copyright. It wouldn&#8217;t be the Worldcon&#8217;s job to issue a translation, if that&#8217;s what you mean.</p>
